on to a trend towards genera-specific hemoplasma genotypes. The present study contributes to the knowledge of the wide diversity of hemoplasmas in vampire bats.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "De Mello, Vict\u00f3ria Valente Califre", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "De Oliveira, Laryssa Borges", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Coelho, Taciana Fernandes Souza Barbosa", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lee, Daniel Antonio Braga", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Franco, Eliz Oliveira", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Machado, Rosangela Zacarias", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Andr\u00e9, Marcos Rog\u00e9rio", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/53840355addbe819872bb8d7e7e5026f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/11af520cac9ed4d10429e4e1830c651863320f5e4b62fd8167da77fbe4156967", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/M3MG959A", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/M3MG959A", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/d7ca551ef7b06bd74418f971822d3646!/b16588-19152", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "102127", "title": "Comparative Immunology, Microbiology and Infectious Diseases", "volume": "106"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "